% Handwritten A0 — Milestone 1 corpus (refund_handler)

<requirements>
Implement a refund handler for a payment API.
Only active users may receive refunds.
The same refund request id must be idempotent: repeating it returns the same outcome.
When the user is unauthorized, reject the refund.
When the refund amount is invalid, reject the refund.
Successful refunds must return a receipt identifier.
</requirements>
